io.scanbot.sdk.ui.utils

Interface ConnectablePresenter<View extends StatelessView<?>>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BarcodeCameraPresenter, BatchBarcodeListPresenter, CameraPresenter, CrossViewStatePresenter, EditPolygonPresenter, HealthInsuranceCardCameraPresenter, IdCardCameraPresenter, IdCardFieldListPresenter, LicensePlateScannerPresenter, MRZCameraPresenter, MultipleObjectsDetectorPresenter, NfcPassportPresenter, TextDataScannerPresenter, WorkflowCameraPresenter

    public ConnectablePresenter<View extends StatelessView<?>>

    Presents data to views. Abstracts business logic from views. Must be used only by main thread. Default state is Paused.

    • Method Detail

      • resume

        void resume(@NotNull
            View view)

        Called when presenter should resume operations.

        Parameters:
        view - which will be used to display data.

      • pause

        void pause()

        Called when presenter should pause operation. This is the default state. At this state view will never be updated even if some long-running operation completes after this point.

      • back

        boolean back()

        Called when presenter should navigate back.

        Returns:
        true if call is processed, false if call should be processed by parent or not supported.
